news.title: SC directs Rajasthan government to take stringent measures to stop illegal mining of bajri
news.para: The top court also directed the state government to grant mining leases in favour of 68 lessees who have obtained environmental clearance without further delay.

news.title: HCC's net profit drops 80% to Rs 30.88 crore in Q4 FY22
news.para: Total income during the quarter under review stood at Rs 2,946.16 crore, compared to Rs 2,398.38 crore in the year-ago period. Total expenses increased to Rs 2,884.36 crore from Rs 2,618.48 crore earlier.

news.title: Nashik civic body serves fresh reminders to 25 builders
news.para: NMC had sent notices to builders involved in 65 projects that came up over 4,000 sq metre of land. Only 35 builders have furnished information related to the project.

news.title: Kolkata: ED raids Abhijata Constructions, promoters in money laundering case
news.para: The money laundering case against the company and its promoters stems from several Kolkata Police FIRs where numerous home buyers alleged "non delivery of homes by the company in spite of getting full payments from the buyers," the ED said in a statement.

news.title: Owner-tenant dispute on deposit can go to arbritrator: HC
news.para: HC held arbitration can be invoked as the dispute was over a claim of damages in a security deposit refund and not rent money or any other monthly charge.

news.title: Zhongliang Holdings' debt woes worsen as sales, yuan weaken
news.para: The Shanghai-based company has struggled to sell enough houses amid a sustained property downturn in China or secure refinancing to pay investors who are due full redemption on their bonds in May and July.

news.title: UP-NCR brick kiln owners can deposit annual fees till May 31
news.para: Officials said that the National Green Tribunal had curbed the activities that added to air pollution levels in the national capital and neighbouring districts. Subsequently, brick kiln operators did not deposit the annual regulating fees.

news.title: Punjab & Haryana HC questions HSVP over alternative plots
news.para: Last week, while expressing displeasure over the unprecedented delay of around 30 years in allotment of an alternative plot to one of the allottees, the HC had directed HSVP to provide details of all allotments made in the past three decades to the similarly placed persons.

news.title: Hyderabad: Residents fume over illegal construction
news.para: GHMC officials admitted in the high court that the construction was illegal as permission was granted for silt + 2 floors only.

news.title: LIC Housing Finance revises rate of interest on home loans to 6.9%
news.para: The new interest rate on home loans starts from 6.9% with effect from May 13, 2022. The interest rate has been changed from 6.7% to 6.9%.

news.title: Top 100 property tax defaulters owe Coimbatore corporation Rs 45 crore
news.para: An official said the corporation could not collect taxes from at least half of the defaulters for years as cases pending in district courts and the high court are making slow progress.

news.title: Close to Rs 12 lakh crore expenditure on urban schemes since 2014: Housing minister
news.para: "In the ten years of previous government 2004-2014, the total amount of expenditure incurred on all the urban schemes taken together was Rs 1.57 lakh crore," he said.

news.title: RLDA invites bid for residential development in Bareilly
news.para: The complete land area of the project is divided into two parts. In the part A (19660 Sqm) is earmarked for mandatory redevelopment of railway assets and in part B (62780 Sqm) is earmarked for residential development.

news.title: Brigade Enterprises posts Rs 11.63 crore loss in Q4 FY22
news.para: The company's total consolidated income stood at Rs 964.72 crore in Q4 FY22, a growth of 18 per cent from Rs 820.86 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.

news.title: Gurugram: Builders of nine colonies told to share property info in a week
news.para: The colonies that have received DTCP’s approval for takeover by the MCG include Rosewood City, Greenwood City, Malibu Town, Ardee City, Sushant Lok-2 & 3, Mayfield Garden, Vipul Gardens and Uppal Southend.
